node.text:
I love running for the simplicity, the suffering, the rollercoaster, the possibilities, and the memories created with friends. And the post-run snacks. 😊 
•••
Had a great time with @kodiakcakes getting some footage for this short video. Thanks, team! Soaking up these views with you all was so fun. 🏜
•••
#deweytoit #kodiakcakes

🧟‍♀️😨 “You’re fine. This is fine. You’re fine. This is fine. You’re fine. You’re fine. You’re fine. You’re fine.” 🔁 Pretty sure this was my face the entire last climb at @utmbmontblanc. My legs were toast and I was deeeeeep in the cave doing bigtime chiseling on some new tunnels. 👷‍♀️⛏⛏
•••
📷 @chillie.1

node.text:
Going into UTMB, I knew that I wanted to finish the loop. No matter what, we wanted that 100 mile adventure. I felt mentally fired up to push, and physically ready to take on the mountain trails of @utmbmontblanc. Once the race started, it was simple: forward motion, problem-solving, and remembering which country I was in so I knew how to say “thank you” in the correct language. 😊 Thanks for all the cheers and support out on course and online! This community is incredible! 🙏
•••
📷 @davidmillerphotography_
•••
#deweytoit #timetoplay #runonemotion #salomonWMN @salomonrunning #suuntorun #gotailwind #kodiakcakes #squirrelsnutbutter #sweetentheburn #toesocksornosocks #adventurestartshere #tanrioutdoors

node.text:
DNF Hardrock. 😔 I’m bummed but also reminded how cool & unpredictable this sport is. Hope to get the chance to try this one again sometime - those mountains were so fun to play in and my legs were so ready to play! 🏔 Stomach issues early turned into bigger issues later, so it looks like we have some reflecting and adjusting to do. Always learning and trying to be better. On to the next!
•••
Congrats to @francois_dhaene on the win and killer Course Record! Allez! And @sabrinaleannstanley for back-to-back wins on this amazing, tough course! 💪🎉
•••
📷 @trailjunkiephotos
•••
